The paper deals with solving constraint satisfaction problems using answer set programming, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of local consistency properties, which is a topic in logic and set theory (cs.LO). Additionally, the paper involves programming language concepts such as translation and reformulation (cs.PL). The use of constraints and solving algorithms also relates to data structures (cs.DS) and software engineering (cs.SE).
